messages.message: Is there any reason not to click “advanced mode”, ie does it cost more?
+1 would be good to add an info icon with tooltip maybe that lets user know advanced model uses gpt 4 and uses more tokens or takes longer

so here it’s actually using 2 different pipelines. basic mode lets you have provenance and structured output. Advanced mode is a “jailbreak” that let’s you send more pure prompts to gpt. It doesn’t change the model used
